_sText:
Creator of the map: Tony Clarke Hawco.
Give credit if used.


I know it's probably not de_dust2. But I assure you I have thought out how the flow of the map will work. Chaotic at the start, traveling carefully in the middle, and a manhunt at the end. I have made it so any cheap tricks like spawn killing are put to a minimal. This is the first CSS map I have made, and I hope you enjoy it.
